Name: Bullet Art
About the game: Create and Play bullet hell! Very highly customizable bullet hell level editor. Snap levels to a music to make it more interesting. Load youtube video to stream music for the level. Share levels using workshop in game. Practice mode to play level from a specific point. Replay mode to view your play. Uses multithreading to calculate bullets. and some experimental features.. Editor Feature Creating Patterns Create what you want
